{"type": "article", "id": 30996, "title": "日本最大免税店亏损，以及，Alexander Wang 秋冬系列主打 Hip-Hop | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-15T02:42:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 2969, "name": "Vivienne Westwood"}, {"id": 28990, "name": "Diptyque"}, {"id": 31498, "name": "Adidas Originals NMD"}, {"id": 31500, "name": "RMK"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 31499, "name": "WAOX"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160815091905LcCy5vpHYJ3Kiubz.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/uniqlos-sixth-collaboration-with-ines-de-la-fressange-explores-paris-in-the-sixties-10506009/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>优衣库将发布与 Inès de La Fressange 合作的第六个系列</b></a> | 早在 2014 年，法国模特、服装设计师 Inès de La Fressange 就签署了与优衣库的合约。近日，优衣库宣布了最新的这个系列的主题为 “Paris at the Height of 1960s Fashion”。将于 9 月 9 日开始，在各大优衣库旗舰店和官方网店上架。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/business/2016/08/12/00021236.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>日本最大的免税店 LAOX 上半年度亏损严重</b></a> |  由于受到日元升值影响，访日游客骤减，日本国内最大的免税店 LAOX 2016 上半年亏损 4.64 亿日元，去年同期则盈利 46 亿日元。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/mass-off-price/liverpool-targets-14-percent-revenue-hike-suburbia-10506556/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>墨西哥最大的百货集团 Liverpool 预计收入将增加 14%</b></a> | 在斥资 10.4 亿美元买下连锁服装品牌 Suburbia 之后，Liverpool 调整了它的收入预期，至 62 亿美元，上涨了 14%。Liverpool 将同时运营 233 个店铺，成为继西班牙的 Inditex 之后，墨西哥第二大的零售集团。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/alexander-wang-awarded-90-million-in-anti-counterfeit-and-cybersquatting-case-10506074/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Alexander Wang 获赔 9 千万美元</b></a> | 近日，美国联邦地区法院宣判，Alexander Wang 在假冒商标和域名案中获赔 9 千万美元。这是 Alexander Wang 第一次提起的诉讼，其涉案被告最少有 45 人，涉及到域名被抢注的网站达到 459 个。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/fashion/2016/08/12/00021235.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Vivienne Westwood 统合女装男装部门并退出时装周</b></a> | Vivienne Westwood 将于 2017 年 1 月开始，在伦敦男装周上发布合并后的全新秋冬男女装系列。并宣布退出 2016 年 9 月的 2017 伦敦时装周，不再发布原定的春夏女装秀。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/alexander-wangs-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang 发布 2016 秋冬系列</a>。本次秋冬新品的主题是 Hip-Hop，包括了 Hoodie 帽衫、工装口袋夹克、宽松运动裤、oversize 卫衣等款式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092433nAC1JaRXWTLUEuG7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092423xZLTt1MQAUmEz2qO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092415dE4ei53oHqJlgZSn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092052ChHsEfBQipI4Yanz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608150920453HhOpC08M1u7VcRb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/adidas-originals-nmd-women-aug\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adidas Originals NMD</a> 系列推出了五款女生配色，将于 8 月 18 日正式上架。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092517MumFbDRGIEzPiNfe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092511rgeZ34NpIqS5m6vK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092504D39Ljo6MVl5PQUBW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092452ZyEujJlkPrDUCg9R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608150924438t9L4QeVmlvhzYwM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>香氛品牌 Diptyque 更新了它的护肤系列 <a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/beauty/buro-loves/face-first-diptyque-introduces-l-art-du-soin.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">L'Art Du Soin</a>。此次新加入了面霜、美容油和润唇膏。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092539JfgBj7SxW4YECv0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.406250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092533pxrzfT13JjCIB0sM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.406250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092526N1OMInmgyCDqKGoV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.406250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">另外，推荐前 Y’s 设计师藤内裕司的原创品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/wislom-2016-aw\" rel=\"nofollow\"> WISLOM</a>。该品牌首季只推出了限量版外套系列，强调素材的使用，全部运用了藤内裕司自己研发的材质。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092626f96BLmjYetUo4F12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092616RKJCt1bu0QpFDG4L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815092606PcAyMr7Fz4iOEo8n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608150925569lum2FNrvtpJyoik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">日本美妆品牌 RMK 发布 2016 秋冬季新妆容。这一次是主题是 The Silver Screen，以昔日好莱坞女星为灵感，打造犹如镁光灯下的时尚妆容。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815100454D9mAGQj2XcN53gOf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815100447Ue1SKz0M7fgPOxuI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706055\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815100440NSRAM90gzIJhkiaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815100429Bk896vunfUJWYcqx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641791\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}